headline: Republic Services (RSG): Net Margin Tops Consensus, Reinforcing Bullish Narratives on Value and Profit Quality
summary: Republic Services (RSG) reported a net profit margin of 12.8% for the period, edging above last year's 12.5%. Over the past five years, the company’s earnings have grown at an annual rate of 15.7%, though recent earnings growth came in at 6.9%, trailing its longer-term average. Revenue growth is forecast at 5.2% annually, which is slower than the broader US market’s 10.3%.
